This add-on allows to resize images using click and drag in the editor. Please go to https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-resize-image for the whole list of feature and to report bugs.

This add-on is supported by a [Kickstarter](https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/arthurmilchior/image-resizing-in-anki/). You can donate no it to reach the next goal: resizing images in reviewer.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fpXTCDxFbeM&feature=emb_title

